{"tid":1251155,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"Arduino自製Display面板","createTime":"2019-06-22T11:41:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-22T11:56:54.000Z","uid":153427,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6f67afe1ba4ebd31875f8fe208ff2d772cc1ab92","tid":1251155,"uid":153427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T11:41:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/xwfbdoyq\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fxwfbdoyq&h=b83fe077&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/zpy8nihw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fzpy8nihw&h=bfd27ddc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/3yamqkbg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F3yamqkbg&h=22eb6ea5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n材料：<br />\nArduino一塊（一定要Mega328P/32U4/Mega2560等5V板）<br />\n淘寶LCD1602連IIC控制板一塊<br />\n<br />\n接法：<br />\nArduino - LCD<br />\nSCL, SDA, 5V, GND跟返去駁就得<br />\n我就自己再剪左條USB線直接插Motherboard<br />\n<br />\nCode：<br />\nArduino Scratch (需要用LiquidCrystal Library，自備) - <a href=\"https://www.pastiebin.com/5d0e130de3a04\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pastiebin.com%2F5d0e130de3a04&d=ahpQ5aMQEo4h8Mt%2B3j6t3p0arUk5yypfOu6hIjalRP8%3D&h=02ee7164\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.pastiebin.com/5d0e130de3a04</a><br />\n自行留意板既IIC Address：有機會係0x20或0x27 自己改，係頭幾行有comment<br />\n<br />\nUbuntu Python Demo Script - <a href=\"https://www.pastiebin.com/5d0e137245507\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pastiebin.com%2F5d0e137245507&d=ahpQ5aMQEo4h8Mt%2B3j6t3p0arUk5yypfOu6hIjalRP8%3D&h=314e0544\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.pastiebin.com/5d0e137245507</a><br />\nPython3，需要裝pyserial<br />\n<br />\n用途：<br />\nArduino Code就係 - 一路讀住Serial Port再Display任何字，所以可以用作<br />\n- NAS顯示IP，溫度<br />\n- Linux PC顯示IP，溫度，任何野<br />\n由於本人唔用Windows所以冇整Windows Python Script<br />\n有興趣既人歡迎改Code"},{"pid":"94b9eb5aa154a3b8e7e3ba79c901bfe4cba62770","tid":1251155,"uid":153427,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T11:48:33.000Z","msg":"FreeNAS版本 - 自帶Port detection<br />\n插好Arduino係terminal行python3 script.py即可<br />\n至於點自動行，自己諗掂佢啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.pastiebin.com/5d0e150298453\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pastiebin.com%2F5d0e150298453&d=ahpQ5aMQEo4h8Mt%2B3j6t3p0arUk5yypfOu6hIjalRP8%3D&h=02765a30\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.pastiebin.com/5d0e150298453</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4eQYyiU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4eQYyiU.png&h=caf28fe9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e12c3474467c1125d0dc5e67fb5df7c51249940e","tid":1251155,"uid":34145,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T11:56:54.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然 有d 簡單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}